                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">White</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">St.
                                        Petersburg</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-07-02"><hi rend="italic">July 2,
                                1894</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Your cipher telegram received. Case shall be attended to at once
                            fully.</p>
